  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Dimensions",
      "body": "44\"w x 24\"d x 30\"h",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/77a0324630a1e60a.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 1",
      "body": "Step 1: Make the side frames. Attach the horizontal piece to the legs using wood glue and 2 ½” pocket hole screws.\nMake 3.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/4f6b6f100627239c.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 2",
      "body": "Step 2: Make the side panels. Attach the side panel wall to the frame using wood glue and 1 ¼” pocket hole screws.\nMake 2.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/77a2abb97a71c97c.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 3",
      "body": "Step 3: Attach the short cross supports to the interior side of one wall panel. I suggest placing the metal drawer unit temporarily in position to ensure proper spacing.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/7ee65a0141ef2726.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 4",
      "body": "Step 4: Attach the other side wall panel to the cross supports using 1 ¼” pocket hole screws.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/d88ac2a543df0206.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 5",
      "body": "Step 5: Construct the desk base by attaching the long cross supports from the open frame to the side wall panel.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/626302d92dbe3666.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 6",
      "body": "Step 6: Attach the desk top the frame using countersunk screws.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/18f322934da79242.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 7",
      "body": "Step 7: Insert the metal drawer unit frame and attach using ½” lath screws at all four corners.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/8f1c03807188a0ed.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 8",
      "body": "Step 8: Attach the open shelf ledge to the legs using 1 ¼” pocket hole screws.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/aacb982f843bd7d4.webp"
    },
    {
      "title": "Step 9",
      "body": "Step 9: Attach the backing to the frame using 1 ¼” finish nails.",
      "image": "https://pub-b845b7e7b4924e4d8f2520661b54734d.r2.dev/plans/630f9adfc643b1d1.webp"
    }
  ],
